BT /F1 24 Tf 50 700 Td (Chapter 1: Introduction to Habits) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 50 660 Td (Habits are the small decisions you make and actions you perform every day.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 50 640 Td (According to researchers at Duke University, habits account for about 40 percent of) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 50 620 Td (our behaviors on any given day. Your life today is essentially the sum of your habits.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 50 580 Td (How you spend your mornings, how productive you are at work, how much you exercise) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 50 560 Td (all of these things are the result of habits you have developed over time.) Tj ET
